    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a crisp autumn morning, the sun glinting off a mirror-finish coat of midnight blue. This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule. Every stitch in the hand-finished leather tells a story of elegance, while the engine hums with the refined confidence of a predator at rest. To sit behind the wheel is to step into a world where craftsmanship reigned supreme. It\u2019s a mechanical symphony, preserved in breathtaking harmony, waiting for a driver who understands that true beauty is timeless. This is your invitation to own a legend, a rare survivor that turns every mundane commute into a grand tour.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle preserved in pristine, showroom condition. This unit has been curated for the most discerning collector, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains as fresh as the day it was manufactured. Meticulously maintained and strictly garaged, it offers a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber. With its impeccable service history and uncompromising presentation, this car stands as a testament to automotive excellence. Experience the peak of performance and luxury in a package that is, quite simply, beyond reproach.",
      "price": 49500.0,
